<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>진행중인 이벤트 - GS25</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/plugin.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>진행중인 이벤트</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
			<button type="button" id="qrpop" class="btnQr" title="QR코드 팝업 열기">QR코드</button>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content gs25">
		<!-- 내용 -->
		<div class="boardView line">
			<div class="viewTit">
				<h2 class="tit">스탬프(누적) 이벤트 텍스트 텍스트 텍스트 텍스트 텍스트 텍스트 텍스트</h2>
				<span class="txt"><span class="data">2019-10-01 ~ 2019-10-31</span></span>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="grade">VIP이상</span>
					<div class="btnCon">
						<button type="button" class="btnRcmd">추천인</button>
						<button type="button" class="btnShare">공유하기</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="eventCon">
				<!-- BOS image component -->
				<div class="cp_img">
					<img src="../../image/tmp/img_tmp_event.jpg" alt="대체텍스트">
				</div>
				<!-- //BOS image component -->
				<div class="situationCon line">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h3 class="titDep1">나의 초대 현황</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="textCon">
						<p><strong class="color01">5</strong>명 초대한 친구 중에<br><strong class="color01">0</strong>명이 가입하셨습니다.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="rankCon line">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h3 class="titDep1">친구 가입 순위</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="rankList">
						<div class="title">
							<p>나의 순위 <strong class="color01">14</strong>위</p>
						</div>
						<ul class="list">
							<li>
								<span class="tit"><strong>1</strong>위</span>
								<span class="total">50명</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="tit"><strong>2</strong>위</span>
								<span class="total">41명</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="tit"><strong>3</strong>위</span>
								<span class="total">26명</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="txt"><p class="bl">순위는 전날까지의 집계수로 표시됩니다.</p></div>
				</div>
				<div class="inviteCon line">
					<div class="titArea">
						<h3 class="titDep1">친구 초대</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="inputCon">
						<div class="inputSel">
							<span class="activeInput">
								<label for="phoneNum">핸드폰 번호<em>(숫자만 입력)</em></label>
								<input type="number" id="phoneNum">
								<button type="button" class="delete">입력 내용 삭제</button>
							</span>
							<button type="button" class="btnTS btnM color">연락처검색</button>
						</div>
						<ul class="bl">
							<li>친구의 휴대폰번호를 직접 입력하거나, 연락처 검색 버튼을 통해 휴대폰에 저장된 번호를 선택하세요.</li>
							<li>휴대폰번호는 숫자만 입력 가능합니다.</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="btnArea">
		                	<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">친구 초대하기</button>
		                </div>
		            </div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--//내용 -->
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>